{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881102756,"sessionID":"ses_2853d982fffe05VvFNh3Ebe799","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac3175e0011htK7iLMFjf2X3","messageID":"msg_d7ac30cf8001LAOpFicQsxuYIx","sessionID":"ses_2853d982fffe05VvFNh3Ebe799","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_28466bc6cbb24cc3bf22e40c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/delta-spec.md","offset":100,"limit":200},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/manifests/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n100:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]`\n101:   - `resources: [\"codeinterpreters/status\"]`, `verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]`\n102:   - `resources: [\"codeinterpreters/finalizers\"]`, `verbs: [\"update\"]`\n103: \n104: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRole AgentRuntime permissions\n105: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n106: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n107: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n108:   - `apiGroups: [\"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"]`\n109:   - `resources: [\"agentruntimes\"]`\n110:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]`\n111:   - `resources: [\"agentruntimes/status\"]`\n112:   - `verbs: [\"update\", \"patch\"]`\n113: \n114: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRole core resources\n115: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n116: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n117: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n118:   - `apiGroups: [\"\"]`\n119:   - `resources: [\"pods\", \"secrets\"]`\n120:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]`\n121: \n122: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRole token review\n123: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n124: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n125: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n126:   - `apiGroups: [\"authentication.k8s.io\"]`\n127:   - `resources: [\"tokenreviews\"]`\n128:   - `verbs: [\"create\"]`\n129: \n130: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole creation\n131: - **GIVEN** the manifest `clusterroles/volcano-scheduler.yaml` is applied\n132: - **WHEN** `kubectl apply -f clusterroles/volcano-scheduler.yaml` is executed\n133: - **THEN** a ClusterRole named `volcano-agent-scheduler` SHALL be created\n134: \n135: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole CRD permissions\n136: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n137: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n138: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n139:   - `apiGroups: [\"apiextensions.k8s.io\"]`\n140:   - `resources: [\"customresourcedefinitions\"]`\n141:   - `verbs: [\"create\", \"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]`\n142: \n143: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole pod permissions\n144: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n145: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n146: - **THEN** it SHALL include comprehensive pod permissions:\n147:   - `resources: [\"pods\", \"pods/status\", \"pods/binding\", \"pods/disruptionbudgets\"]`\n148:   - `resources: [\"persistentvolumeclaims\", \"persistentvolumes\"]`\n149:   - `resources: [\"nodes\", \"namespaces\", \"services\", \"replicationcontrollers\"]`\n150: \n151: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole scheduling permissions\n152: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n153: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n154: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n155:   - `apiGroups: [\"scheduling.k8s.io\"]`\n156:   - `resources: [\"priorityclasses\"]`\n157:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]`\n158:   - `apiGroups: [\"scheduling.incubator.k8s.io\", \"scheduling.volcano.sh\"]`\n159:   - `resources: [\"podgroups\"]`\n160:   - `verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\", \"update\"]`\n161: \n162: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole storage permissions\n163: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n164: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n165: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n166:   - `apiGroups: [\"storage.k8s.io\"]`\n167:   - `resources: [\"storageclasses\", \"csinodes\", \"csidrivers\", \"csistoragecapacities\", \"volumeattachments\"]`\n168:   - `verbs: [\"list\", \"watch\"]`\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRole configmap permissions\n171: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRole is created\n172: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n173: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n174:   - `apiGroups: [\"\"]`\n175:   - `resources: [\"configmaps\"]`\n176:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"delete\", \"update\"]`\n177: \n178: ---\n179: \n180: ### REQ-031.3: ClusterRoleBinding Manifests\n181: \n182: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide standalone ClusterRoleBinding manifests binding ClusterRoles to ServiceAccounts.\n183: \n184: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRoleBinding creation\n185: - **GIVEN** the manifest `clusterrolebindings/workloadmanager.yaml` is applied\n186: - **WHEN** `kubectl apply -f clusterrolebindings/workloadmanager.yaml` is executed\n187: - **THEN** a ClusterRoleBinding named `workloadmanager` SHALL be created\n188: \n189: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRoleBinding subject\n190: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRoleBinding is created\n191: - **WHEN** subjects are validated\n192: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n193:   - `kind: ServiceAccount`\n194:   - `name: workloadmanager`\n195:   - `namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}` (or target namespace)\n196: \n197: #### Scenario: WorkloadManager ClusterRoleBinding roleRef\n198: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRoleBinding is created\n199: - **WHEN** roleRef is validated\n200: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n201:   - `kind: ClusterRole`\n202:   - `name: workloadmanager`\n203:   - `apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io`\n204: \n205: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRoleBinding creation\n206: - **GIVEN** the manifest `clusterrolebindings/volcano-scheduler.yaml` is applied\n207: - **WHEN** `kubectl apply -f clusterrolebindings/volcano-scheduler.yaml` is executed\n208: - **THEN** a ClusterRoleBinding named `volcano-agent-scheduler-role` SHALL be created\n209: \n210: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRoleBinding subject\n211: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRoleBinding is created\n212: - **WHEN** subjects are validated\n213: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n214:   - `kind: ServiceAccount`\n215:   - `name: volcano-agent-scheduler`\n216:   - `namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}` (or target namespace)\n217: \n218: #### Scenario: Volcano Scheduler ClusterRoleBinding roleRef\n219: - **GIVEN** the ClusterRoleBinding is created\n220: - **WHEN** roleRef is validated\n221: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n222:   - `kind: ClusterRole`\n223:   - `name: volcano-agent-scheduler`\n224:   - `apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io`\n225: \n226: ---\n227: \n228: ### REQ-031.4: Role Manifests (Namespace-Scoped)\n229: \n230: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide namespace-scoped Role manifests for Router component.\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: Router Role creation\n233: - **GIVEN** the manifest `roles/router.yaml` is applied\n234: - **WHEN** `kubectl apply -f roles/router.yaml` is executed\n235: - **THEN** a Role named `agentcube-router` SHALL be created in the target namespace\n236: \n237: #### Scenario: Router Role secret permissions\n238: - **GIVEN** the Role is created\n239: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n240: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n241:   - `apiGroups: [\"\"]`\n242:   - `resources: [\"secrets\"]`\n243:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]`\n244: \n245: #### Scenario: Router Role configmap permissions\n246: - **GIVEN** the Role is created\n247: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n248: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n249:   - `apiGroups: [\"\"]`\n250:   - `resources: [\"configmaps\"]`\n251:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]`\n252: \n253: #### Scenario: Router Role pod permissions\n254: - **GIVEN** the Role is created\n255: - **WHEN** rules are validated\n256: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n257:   - `apiGroups: [\"\"]`\n258:   - `resources: [\"pods\"]`\n259:   - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\"]`\n260: \n261: ---\n262: \n263: ### REQ-031.5: RoleBinding Manifests (Namespace-Scoped)\n264: \n265: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide namespace-scoped RoleBinding manifests binding Roles to ServiceAccounts.\n266: \n267: #### Scenario: Router RoleBinding creation\n268: - **GIVEN** the manifest `rolebindings/router.yaml` is applied\n269: - **WHEN** `kubectl apply -f rolebindings/router.yaml` is executed\n270: - **THEN** a RoleBinding named `agentcube-router` SHALL be created in the target namespace\n271: \n272: #### Scenario: Router RoleBinding subject\n273: - **GIVEN** the RoleBinding is created\n274: - **WHEN** subjects are validated\n275: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n276:   - `kind: ServiceAccount`\n277:   - `name: agentcube-router`\n278:   - `namespace: {{ .Release.Namespace }}` (or target namespace)\n279: \n280: #### Scenario: Router RoleBinding roleRef\n281: - **GIVEN** the RoleBinding is created\n282: - **WHEN** roleRef is validated\n283: - **THEN** it SHALL include:\n284:   - `kind: Role`\n285:   - `name: agentcube-router`\n286:   - `apiGroup: rbac.authorization.k8s.io`\n287: \n288: ---\n289: \n290: ### REQ-031.6: Namespace Management\n291: \n292: **Requirement:** The system SHALL provide namespace manifest and support namespace creation before RBAC application.\n293: \n294: #### Scenario: Namespace manifest creation\n295: - **GIVEN** the manifest `namespace.yaml` is applied\n296: - **WHEN** `kubectl apply -f namespace.yaml` is executed\n297: - **THEN** a namespace named `agentcube-system` SHALL be created\n298: \n299: #### Scenario: Namespace metadata\n\n(Showing lines 100-299 of 578. Use offset=300 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"  - `verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"create\", \"update\", \"patch\", \"delete\"]`\n  - `resources: [\"codeinterpreters/status\"]`, `verbs: [\"get\", \"update\", \"patch\"]`\n  - `resources: [\"codeinterpreters/finalizers\"]`, `verbs: [\"update\"]`\n\n###