{"type":"text","timestamp":1775881138337,"sessionID":"ses_2853d982fffe05VvFNh3Ebe799","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac38636001Ow0M67vaFTOqiw","messageID":"msg_d7ac373d5001J0CXxYfAhSF06x","sessionID":"ses_2853d982fffe05VvFNh3Ebe799","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of the AR-031 RBAC configuration work, here is the summary:\n\n## AR-031 — RBAC 配置 (SA/Role/Binding) 完成总结\n\n### ✅ Completed (已完成)\n\n**Helm Chart 内 RBAC 资源:**\n1. **WorkloadManager RBAC** (`templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`)\n   - ServiceAccount: `workloadmanager`\n   - ClusterRole: `workloadmanager` (完整的 Sandbox/CodeInterpreter/AgentRuntime 权限)\n   - ClusterRoleBinding: 绑定 SA 到 ClusterRole\n\n2. **Router RBAC** (`templates/rbac-router.yaml`)\n   - ServiceAccount: `agentcube-router`\n   - Role: namespace-scoped, Secrets 读写权限\n   - RoleBinding: 绑定 SA 到 Role\n   - 支持 `.Values.router.rbac.create` 条件开关\n\n3. **测试覆盖**\n   - `tests/workloadmanager-rbac_test.yaml` - WorkloadManager RBAC 测试\n   - `tests/rbac-router_test.yaml` - Router RBAC 测试 (8 个测试场景)\n\n---\n\n### ⏸️ Deferred (已延期)\n\n**独立 RBAC Manifest 目录结构** (delta-spec.md 中定义):\n- `manifests/rbac/namespace.yaml` - Namespace 清单\n- `manifests/rbac/serviceaccounts/*.yaml` - 独立 SA 文件\n- `manifests/rbac/clusterroles/*.yaml` - 独立 ClusterRole 文件\n- `manifests/rbac/clusterrolebindings/*.yaml` - 独立 ClusterRoleBinding 文件\n- `manifests/rbac/roles/router.yaml` - 独立 Router Role\n- `manifests/rbac/rolebindings/router.yaml` - 独立 Router RoleBinding\n- `manifests/rbac/rbac.yaml` - 组合清单\n- `manifests/rbac/rbac-cleanup.yaml` - 清理清单\n- `manifests/rbac/validate-rbac.sh` - 验证脚本\n- `manifests/rbac/README.md` - 使用文档\n\n**Volcano Scheduler RBAC** - 未找到独立的 SA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding 文件\n\n**Open Questions 未决议:**\n1. 是否支持通过 overlay 文件进行细粒度权限定制\n2. 验证脚本是否集成 CI/CD\n3. 是否需要 PodSecurityPolicy/PodSecurityStandard 绑定\n4. 是否需要分级 RBAC profile (minimal/standard/full)","time":{"start":1775881138324,"end":1775881138324}}}
